snippet.title: Dune Strider - Early Access Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Dune Strider is an Adventure-Strategy Game in which you, the player, take command of a merchant controlling a Sand-Barge in a desert and use it to travel and explore the land around you. The road to settlements to sell your goods is filled with dangers and opportunities.

Wishlist/Download us on steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1768590/Dune_Strider/

Follow us on our Socials:
Discord: https://discord.gg/eGDpJUvyrs
Twitter: https://twitter.com/dunestriderbuas
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/DuneStrider/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dunestrider_official/?hl=en

Music: Crossing The High Desert - by Humans Win
